Working With Profiles
```
avatar.profile.get()
```
– fetches and caches the IPFS JSON referenced by
cidV0
```
avatar.profile.update(profile)
```
– pins new metadata and updates the NameRegistry digest; useful for avatar name/description/image changes.
```
sdk.register.asHuman(inviter, profileOrCid)
```
– automatically uses the Profiles service when a plain object is supplied, so invitees do not need prior CID knowledge.
