Trust & Transfers
Establish trust through
```
avatar.trust.add('0xFriend...', expiry?)
```
, remove trust via
```
avatar.trust.remove
```
, and inspect relationships using
```
avatar.trust.getAll()
```
```
avatar.trust.isTrusting
```
Transfer CRC with
```
avatar.transfer.direct('0xRecipient...', 25n * 10n ** 18n)
```
for simple paths, or
```
```
to opt into wrapped balances, token filters, or encoded metadata.
Replenish personal (unwrapped) CRC by converting wrapped holdings with
```
avatar.balances.replenish()
```
; the SDK uses the pathfinder to determine the optimal flow back to the avatar’s personal token.
